    "body": "@rauljordan On the validator it shows the status during the new assignment. But after the validator is slashed / exited there is no new assignment so it doesnt show the status. See below the moment when it was slashed and went from ACTIVE to slashed / exited.\r\n\r\n`[2020-04-22 11:55:12]  INFO validator: Previous epoch aggregated voting summary attestationInclusionPercentage=1.00 correctlyVotedHeadPercentage=1.00 correctlyVotedSourcePercentage=1.00 correctlyVotedTargetPercentage=1.00 epoch=992\r\n[2020-04-22 11:55:12]  INFO validator: New assignment attesterSlot=31794 committeeIndex=0 epoch=993 pubKey=0x93f571fdf26b status=ACTIVE validatorIndex=10193\r\n[2020-04-22 11:58:52]  INFO validator: Submitted new attestations AggregatorIndices=[] AttesterIndices=[10193] BeaconBlockRoot=0x0032d69240b5 CommitteeIndex=0 Slot=31794 SourceEpoch=992 SourceRoot=0xf214bdea8168 TargetEpoch=993 TargetRoot=0xcafc41f38e63\r\n[2020-04-22 12:01:36]  INFO validator: Previous epoch voting summary correctlyVotedHead=true correctlyVotedSource=true correctlyVotedTarget=true epoch=993 inclusionDistance=1 inclusionSlot=31734 newBalance=32.071141931 oldBalance=32.071065906 percentChange=0.00024% pubKey=0x93f571fdf26baf24`\r\n\r\nAfter a few minutes it also shows that the balance has been reduced. \r\n\r\n`[2020-04-22 12:08:00]  INFO validator: Previous epoch voting summary correctlyVotedHead=true correctlyVotedSource=true correctlyVotedTarget=true epoch=994 inclusionDistance=1 inclusionSlot=31770 newBalance=31.071081235 oldBalance=31.0711\r\n41931 percentChange=-0.00020% pubKey=0x93f571fdf26baf24`\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nIt goes on with the previous voting summary. no status shown.\r\nYes validator is slashed. \r\nPubKey=0x93f571fdf26baf24\r\nValidator Id = 10193",
